@school = greenwood

### 🔹 1. List Attendance Sessions

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/?class_id=1&date=2025-06-10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

---

### 🔹 2. Create Attendance (Daily)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

{
"class_obj": 1,
"subject": null,
"teacher": 1,
"date": "2025-06-10",
"session_type": "daily",
"records": [
{ "student": 24, "status": "present" },
{ "student": 25, "status": "absent" }
]
}

---

### 🔹 3. Create Attendance (Subject-wise)

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

{
"class_obj": 1,
"subject": 1,
"teacher": 1,
"date": "2025-06-10",
"session_type": "subject",
"records": [
{ "student": 1, "status": "present" },
{ "student": 2, "status": "late" }
]
}

---

### 🔹 4. Get Session Detail

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

---

### 🔹 5. Update Single Record

PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/1/records/2/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

{
"status": "present",
"remarks": "Updated via API"
}

---

### 🔹 6. Finalize Session

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/1/finalize/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

---

### 🔹 7. Class Summary

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/class-summary/?class_id=1&from_date=2025-06-01&to_date=2025-06-30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

---

### 🔹 8. Student Summary

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/student/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}

---

### 🔹 9. Bulk Status (Pre-fill)

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/bulk-status/?class_id=1&date=2025-06-10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-School-Slug: {{school}}
